  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've arrived at a mysterious island, where you take on the appearance of a child!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no grueling work here. All you need to do is to live happily, ever, after… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you've  grown tired of this life, however, could you find your way out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THIS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Neverland! In this game, you are the latest resident to join Neverland, an island offering a relaxing, joyful life for all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a resident of this island, you could:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/316c5b3178f226a3fe368a993a4bd104.avif?t=1739514331\" width=662 height=348 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Explore its many locations:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/99e373c819cfd4741ad9660fce0432ae.avif?t=1739514331\" width=460 height=238 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Socialize with NPCs rich in personalities, and - if situation allows - start a relationship with them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/56e59774d6b749074399ddb66cd3dea8.avif?t=1739514331\" width=660 height=418 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Plant crops and enjoy the harvest：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/d7ddb37d7df676f94a48fe31067e6f2c.avif?t=1739514331\" width=656 height=278 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Make gourmet delights and treat your friends to a feast</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/91bea2a030bbb5e043df669886bc1b61.avif?t=1739514331\" width=604 height=138 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Join holiday celebrations and collect festive awards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/12911e6d4b67af5bdfe3b87e7ce8bb28.avif?t=1739514331\" width=656 height=456 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Find your way out of the island through exploration and deduction - the Grand Finale awaits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And the island holds many more secrets for you to uncover…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've arrived at a mysterious island, where you take on the appearance of a child!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There is no grueling work here. All you need to do is to live happily, ever, after… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you've  grown tired of this life, however, could you find your way out?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THIS GAME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Neverland! In this game, you are the latest resident to join Neverland, an island offering a relaxing, joyful life for all.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a resident of this island, you could:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/316c5b3178f226a3fe368a993a4bd104.avif?t=1739514331\" width=662 height=348 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Explore its many locations:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/99e373c819cfd4741ad9660fce0432ae.avif?t=1739514331\" width=460 height=238 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Socialize with NPCs rich in personalities, and - if situation allows - start a relationship with them!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/56e59774d6b749074399ddb66cd3dea8.avif?t=1739514331\" width=660 height=418 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Plant crops and enjoy the harvest：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/d7ddb37d7df676f94a48fe31067e6f2c.avif?t=1739514331\" width=656 height=278 /></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Make gourmet delights and treat your friends to a feast</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/91bea2a030bbb5e043df669886bc1b61.avif?t=1739514331\" width=604 height=138 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Join holiday celebrations and collect festive awards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3147690/extras/12911e6d4b67af5bdfe3b87e7ce8bb28.avif?t=1739514331\" width=656 height=456 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >·Find your way out of the island through exploration and deduction - the Grand Finale awaits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And the island holds many more secrets for you to uncover…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
